OL,3,CMedics appeal denied over shortcomings
OL,4,Cin care for patient who died
OL,6,FTwo Jersey medics who were found
OL,7,Fguilty of failing to adequately care
OL,8,Ffor a man in the moments before he
OL,9,Fdied have had their appeal denied at
OL,10,FJersey Royal Court.
OL,12,FJohn Sutherland, 66, and Tom Le
OL,13,FSauteur, 36, were found guilty of
OL,14,Fbreaching health and safety laws on
OL,15,FWednesday 26 June 2024.
OL,17,FThe pair were conditionally discharged
OL,18,Fand ordered to pay #500 each in court
OL,19,Fcosts but appealed their sentences.
