OL,4,Cin care for patient who died
OL,6,FSutherland told ITV News they believed
OL,7,Fit was important to attempt an appeal:
OL,9,FThe verdict followed an eight-day
OL,10,Ftrial, where jurats ruled the pair
OL,11,Ffailed to carry out their duties to
OL,12,Fprotect Frazer Irvine, who suffered a
OL,13,Ffatal cardiac arrest in March 2022.
OL,15,FMr Irvine called 999 for himself after
OL,16,Fa suspected pill and alcohol overdose,
OL,17,Fbut his condition worsened once
OL,18,FSutherland and Le Sauteur arrived.
