OL,3,CMedics appeal denied over shortcomings
OL,4,Cin care for patient who died
OL,6,FThe initial guilty verdict garnered
OL,7,Fcriticism from islanders as setting a
OL,8,F"dangerous precedent" for health
OL,9,Fproviders. Hundreds gathered at St
OL,10,FHelier's ambulance station to
OL,11,Fdemonstrate against the decision.
OL,13,FThe pair will now go through an
OL,14,Finternal process to decide whether
OL,15,Fthey will remain in their positions.
